{"tid":299152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鐵怪婦 遇傷健人士即辱罵","createTime":"2017-06-27T00:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T00:43:33.000Z","uid":8129,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd698773901a95c78aaa9c611deeadb786ef9d7","tid":299152,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T00:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/a1ZDqqjHMTtRgyx4eJaYHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/aea06f88181ec6c80d49231acd14f9d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fa1ZDqqjHMTtRgyx4eJaYHA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Faea06f88181ec6c80d49231acd14f9d1&h=4c6bbe83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=t8LTyw%2FSUJumHGMv5hJKhDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b95d2a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】無障礙設施普及，大大幫助傷殘人士融入社會，不過障礙未必來自設施，而是源於無知的偏見。東網讀者報料指，港鐵馬鐵線近日出現一名奇怪婦人，每每向輪椅客出言辱罵。據讀者提供的短片顯示，怪婦在逾兩分鐘內說了「殘廢人」逾80次，在旁乘客亦不值怪婦歧視傷健人士所為，出言反駁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀者提供的短片所見，一名頭戴漁夫帽的中年婦人坐在車廂內，向着疑是正在拍攝的輪椅客，連續辱罵他是「殘廢、殘廢人」，短短2分15秒的短片，婦人連續指罵共86次，行為令人煩厭。有乘客不值怪婦所為，代輪椅客出頭反擊怪婦：「喺公眾場合咁講你咪係廢人一樣！」不過婦人仍繼續辱罵直至落車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據提供短片讀者聲稱，怪婦是馬鐵常客，已連續兩日在馬鐵針對輪椅客出言辱罵，令人憤慨，輪椅友在拍片前亦未有得罪她，難明怪婦的動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5-%E7%89%87-%E9%A6%AC%E9%90%B5%E6%80%AA%E5%A9%A6-%E9%81%87%E5%82%B7%E5%81%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%8D%B3%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5-081447066.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E7%2589%2587-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%2580%25AA%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%2581%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E7%25BD%25B5-081447066.html&d=t8LTyw%2FSUJumHGMv5hJKhDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a8aabdeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5-%E7%89%87-%E9%A6%AC%E9%90%B5%E6%80%AA%E5%A9%A6-%E9%81%87%E5%82%B7%E5%81%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%8D%B3%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5-081447066.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gifyu.com/images/4713ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgifyu.com%2Fimages%2F4713ba.gif&h=1e68824c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbd6ae280c0f33d478c9f7724ec1ba542281cd2f","tid":299152,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"代輪椅客出頭反擊怪婦：「喺公眾場合咁講你咪係廢人一樣！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便屌埋個輪椅"},{"pid":"a03dc7f89f4eb3652a003be5cd4d555b9c79d08e","tid":299152,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T00:14:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22733c68d12bb6093d9a388d3cdca949cdbef176","tid":299152,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T00:40:41.000Z","msg":"廢老 vs 廢人"},{"pid":"8a291308bae25f18525b8d503e56b2a15c760157","tid":299152,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://gifyu.com/images/4713ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgifyu.com%2Fimages%2F4713ba.gif&h=1e68824c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n睇到張圖笑出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}